data.description: Welcome to this adorable 2 story with a great vaulted entry and a huge great room! There are 3 nice size bedrooms - very large primary with ensuite with double sinks, garden tub and walk in shower. There is also a walk in closet! The other bathroom upstairs features a tub/shower combo and single sink. The kitchen is a good size with plenty of counter space and cabinets, stainless steel appliances all stay, plus a large eating space with bay window. The basement has a finished area plus laundry room and storage & crawl. The fenced back yard has a beautiful paver patio with a pergola and firepit. there's a park located in the neighborhood, Olentangy schools, Columbus taxes, close to shopping !
